- tests: test_read_scan_caps_apply_to_reads_not_commands (settings, via the importlib.reload fixture; added the two env keys to ENV_KEYS); test_clickhouse_too_many_rows_or_bytes_returns_400 (errors). 18 pass; ruff clean (env file reformatted).

